<div class="leftFloat"><p class="largeType">"In high school, you can come in late. Here at college if you call your professor, you can come in late, but they don't accept excuses. They tell you that. It's up to you. Class starts on time and you have to be there. It's your responsibility. That's what they tell us."
<br />&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;--Fabiola, 19
